1
00:00:07,289 --> 00:00:09,506
Is it ok if I come in? 
我可以进来吗? 

2
00:00:11,371 --> 00:00:11,916
Yes.
Yes.

3
00:00:16,286 --> 00:00:28,833
Hi. The indisputable fact is that you are sixteen.
Hi. 你现在是16岁,这个事实不容置疑.

4
00:00:30,543 --> 00:00:33,221
We're going to have to work out when you're already sixteen.
我们必须搞清楚你什么时候已经16岁了,

5
00:00:34,045 --> 00:00:35,347
And you're already sixteen.
什么时候才刚刚16岁.

6
00:00:36,163 --> 00:00:40,083
According to you I'm going to be "only" sixteen until I'm ninety.
照你的说法,等我90岁的时候, 也不过才“刚刚”16岁.

7
00:00:40,693 --> 00:00:41,390
You're right, 
你说得对. 

8
00:00:41,902 --> 00:00:45,147
I will be worrying about you longer than you want to know.
我为你操心的时间肯定比你想知道的要长.

9
00:00:45,720 --> 00:00:47,227
But I don't want you to worry. 
可我并不要你操心. 

10
00:00:49,105 --> 00:00:50,925
It's not my fault if you do.
如果你非要为我操心的话这不能怪我.

11
00:00:51,473 --> 00:00:54,360
Well, some situations worry us more than others, Beth. 
Well, 有些情况会比其他情况更令我们担心, Beth. 

12
00:00:54,937 --> 00:00:55,699
This trip is one.
这次旅行就是其中之一.

13
00:00:56,468 --> 00:00:59,430
I'm sorry it's such a disappointment to you. 
如果这令你失望的话,我很抱歉. 

14
00:01:00,344 --> 00:01:02,408
I really am.
真的很抱歉. 

15
00:01:03,396 --> 00:01:05,183
You're just saying that to be nice, Daddy.
你那样说只是想示好, Daddy.

16
00:01:06,211 --> 00:01:07,918
When are you going to let me grow up?
你打算什么时候才让我长大?

17
00:01:08,291 --> 00:01:09,351
Believe me, honey,
相信我, 亲爱的,

18
00:01:09,921 --> 00:01:13,602
soon you'll be doing things you never thought possible.
不久以后你就会做你以前觉得不可能做的事情.

19
00:01:16,646 --> 00:01:19,241
-Say the trip were in two years... -Two years!
-比如说,两年以后再 参加旅行... -两年！

20
00:01:19,624 --> 00:01:21,573
I can't do anything for two years...
那这两年我什么也不能干... 

21
00:01:21,833 --> 00:01:25,686
Listen, listen. You'd be eighteen.
你听我说, 听我说, 那时你就18岁了,

22
00:01:26,520 --> 00:01:27,648
You'd be better prepared. 
准备就更充分了,

23
00:01:27,932 --> 00:01:29,670
There'd be no question about the trip.
出门旅行就不会有问题了. 

24
00:01:30,125 --> 00:01:33,618
So I can do it in two years? 
那我两年以后肯定能去吗? 

25
00:01:35,524 --> 00:01:36,596
Do you promise?
你保证?

26
00:01:37,019 --> 00:01:43,580
Oh boy. You've been doing this since you were a minute old.
Oh boy. 你出生一分钟之的时候就这样了.

27
00:01:44,587 --> 00:01:45,475
What?  
怎样了? 

28
00:01:45,654 --> 00:01:47,437
Wrapping me around your little finger.
把我绕在你的小手指上任你摆布呀. 

29
00:01:47,835 --> 00:01:49,564
Do you promise?
你保证吗?

